    {
      "id": "RgdKDAGzKTR3mT_mHu0LV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 841,
      "y": 650,
      "width": 445.40765380859375,
      "height": 580,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5w",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 316627826,
      "version": 670,
      "versionNonce": 1543580594,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782558970455,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Flows\n\ncommon\nAPI gateway check for authentcation and generate JWT\nOrchestrator check for authorization based on JWT\n\n1. Upload file flow\nUser uploads the file\nCheck if bucket is present\n    if not, create a bucket in object store\n    save metadata\npersist data in object store\nsave metadata\n\n2. Download file flow\nUser selects a objectid and download\nAPI gateway check for authentcation and generate JWT\nOrchestrator check for authorization based on JWT\nCheck for object location in metadata service\nget the location and get the file\nreturn the file\n\n3. List objects in a bukcet\ncheck for bucket metadata\ngo to the location in object storage \nand get all files with /bucket/*\n\n4. see version history\nGet version history from metadata service",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Flows\n\ncommon\nAPI gateway check for authentcation and generate JWT\nOrchestrator check for authorization based on JWT\n\n1. Upload file flow\nUser uploads the file\nCheck if bucket is present\n    if not, create a bucket in object store\n    save metadata\npersist data in object store\nsave metadata\n\n2. Download file flow\nUser selects a objectid and download\nAPI gateway check for authentcation and generate JWT\nOrchestrator check for authorization based on JWT\nCheck for object location in metadata service\nget the location and get the file\nreturn the file\n\n3. List objects in a bukcet\ncheck for bucket metadata\ngo to the location in object storage \nand get all files with /bucket/*\n\n4. see version history\nGet version history from metadata service",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
