      "text": "Availability 99.9 | Durability 11 9s\n\nServers\n1. Multi region deployments\n2. EKS/ EC2\n3. Aurora\n4. multi node deployments\n\n\nData \n1. Replication : 99.9999%\n3 factor replication\n1% AFR\n1 - 0.001^3 = 99.9999",
